@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Forgot Password

actor User
participant "React Frontend" as Frontend
participant "AuthController" as Auth
participant "RaveaDbContext" as DB
participant "EmailService" as Email
participant "Email Provider" as Provider

User -> Frontend : Enter email
Frontend -> Auth : POST /api/auth/forgot-password
Auth -> Auth : Validate email
Auth -> DB : Find user by email
DB --> Auth : User found

Auth -> Auth : Generate 6-digit reset code
Auth -> Auth : Set expiry = Now + 10 minutes
Auth -> DB : Save ResetCode and ResetCodeExpiresAt
DB --> Auth : Save successful

Auth -> Email : SendPasswordResetCodeAsync(email, code)
Email -> Provider : Send reset code email
Provider --> Email : Email sent

Auth --> Frontend : Success message
Frontend --> User : Display confirmation

@enduml
